metadata.name: WAVY FRESH
metadata.description:
Original design by local San Francisco Bay Area artist "inflewince". Designs are first created with different mediums such as; ink, pencil, charcoal, watercolors, oil paints, acrylics, polymers and solvents.

Pre-Digital Medium (PDM); hand-painted acrylic on woodblock panel

Design: illustration of wave with red sky
